headline: FIS to Present at Upcoming Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., September 03, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, will present on Tuesday, September 9th, 2025, at the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference at 1:50pm ET.
